<h2>My Settings</h2>

<p>This screen allows you to customize <%= SITE_NAME %> for your own needs.  You can
change sorting options, display colors, etc.</p>

<p>Administrators use this screen to configure <%= SITE_NAME %> for the whole school.
Configuring the school year, building grading scales, and changing the site name
are some of the things you can do from this screen.</p>

<p>Choose one of the options from the menu on the left side of the screen to 
continue.</p>
